thumb.title: DrUnKeN LoVe fEvEr - ft. Megurine Luka & Kasane Teto - Original Vocaloid Song
thumb.description: Hello, Nico Nico Douga! I'm a producer of a small Vocalo and breakcore called Icy Lapis! This is my first song upload, but you can find more songs on YouTube!
